race.comment: IMMEDIATE (1) is a consistent conveyance who has yet to miss the top-five in eight career outings to date. Is one from one over this course and distance and only needs some luck from the outside draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. Former NSW galloper LINWOOD (2) is having her first run for the new stable but should find this easier than what she faced down south. Follow in if the betting moves are there. ESPRIT DU JOUR (5) is first-up here but has placed two from two when fresh and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. In the mix. DAITANNA (3) draws the inside alley and must be respected from the Bruce camp. One for the multiples. LUCKY LASS (4) next best second-up from the Gollan yard.
